                </div>
                <div class="forecast-body">
                    <p class="forecast-intro">I trade on play-money prediction markets and build websites for real-money ones. My work has been featured in the <em>Evanston Roundtable</em>, the <em>Daily Northwestern</em>, and <em>Capitol Fax</em>.</p>

                    <div class="forecast-stats-bar" id="forecast-stats-bar">
